","tid":2241950,"uid":320293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10ac1cc85ca4f495ba52230e8fd619df12796da3","tid":2241950,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11bd7fdd1ef3ce82b533d9c3fce7d649fc2c740c","tid":2241950,"uid":3180,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"嗰下心痛 想用肉體痛黎分散注意力<br />\n我自己多數就咁咬<br />\n專注痛嗰下 隔一陣就冷靜返<br />\n明白自殘行為係唔健康<br />\n所以隔咗個零月後用其他方法<br />\n靜坐專注呼吸only<br />\n個世界呢一刻發生咩都唔關我事<br />\n一樣calm down到<br />\n個人清醒啲又易諗到新方向<br />\n好多問題都係需要時間黎解決 幾年都有<br />\n好彩最後都解決到<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"靜坐專注呼吸好有效，我用過，有時搭巴士都做。"},{"pid":"acdee9e218aed6453cbb8bd2bbc7908183fa2a6a","tid":2241950,"uid":324823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b37f636dda063f721711f30b94299deadfe92e","tid":2241950,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:17:43.000Z","msg":"仲介手咩年代<br />\n攞完存在感又點<br />\n<br />\n學門手藝啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"介手係分散注意力姐"}]}